# Weather App 🌤️
This project uses the **OpenWeather REST API** to fetch real-time weather data.


## Features
- Search by city name
- Loading & error states
- Displays temperature, humidity, wind, and condition
- Responsive design with Nature Inspired colors

## API Used
- [OpenWeather API](https://openweathermap.org/api)
- Endpoint: `https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/weather`
- Parameters: `q` (city), `units=metric`

## Tech Stack
- HTML5
- CSS3 (Nature Inspired Colors)
- JavaScript (Fetch API)
- Bootstrap (for responsiveness)

